天晚上（3月2日），<em>阿诺拉（Anora）</em>赢得了五场胜利。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/where-to-watch-oscar-nominated-films-uk-3842630">在哪里看英国所有奥斯卡提名电影</a></strong></li></ul><p>第97届奥斯卡金像奖首次由柯南·奥布莱恩（Conan O&#39;Brien）主持，喜剧演员接管吉米·金梅尔（Jimmy Kimmel）的职责。</p><p> <em>Anora</em>证明了这位大冠军，获得了五个奖项，包括最佳照片，Mikey Madison的最佳女演员，Sean Baker的最佳导演，最佳原创剧本和最佳编辑。</p><p> <em>The Brutalist</em> followed behind with three, including Best Actor for Adrien Brody, Best Original Score and Best Cinematography, while <em>Dune: Part Two, Wicked</em> and <em>Emilia Perez</em> took two each.</p><p> The ceremony started with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-host-conan-obrien-pokes-fun-at-emilia-perez-controversy-if-you-are-going-to-tweet-about-the-oscars-my-name-is-jimmy-kimmel-3842827">O&#39;Brien poking fun at the <em>Emilia Perez</em> controversy</a> , while he also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/conan-obrien-makes-kendrick-lamar-drake-joke-at-2025-oscars-dont-worry-im-lawyered-up-3842894">joked about the Drake and Kendrick Lamar feud</a> . Fans were full of <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kieran-culkins-sweary-oscars-acceptance-speech-praised-by-viewers-will-go-down-in-history-as-one-of-the-best-ever-3842844">praise for Kieran Culkin&#39;s Best Supporting Actor speech</a> , as well as <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/best-documentary-oscar-winner-no-other-land-praised-for-moving-speech-on-palestine-3842824">a speech by Documentary Feature winners <em>No Other Land</em></a> , while there were also musical tributes <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2025-watch-the-james-bond-tribute-performance-by-doja-cat-blackpinks-lisa-raye-and-margaret-qualley-3842854">to James Bond</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/watch-the-2025-oscars-tribute-to-quincy-jones-by-queen-latifah-whoopi-goldberg-and-oprah-winfrey-3842917">Quincy Jones</a> .</p><p> This year&#39;s ceremony got a bit of a change-up, with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-2025-oscars-will-not-include-performances-for-best-original-song-category-3831285">no performances for Best Original Song</a> , while the show also honoured Los Angeles following the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">recent devastating wildfires</a> with a nod by O&#39;Brien, who later invited firefighters on to the stage. Harrison Ford also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harrison-ford-no-longer-presenting-at-the-2025-oscars-due-to-illness-3842776">pulled out of presenting</a> ahead of the ceremony due to illness.</p><p> The full list of winners is below:</p><p><b>最佳图片</b></p><p><i><strong>Anora</strong></i> <strong>– WINNER</strong><i><br /></i> <i style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">野蛮主义者<br /></i><i>一个完全未知的<br /></i><i>结论<br /></i><i>沙丘：第二部分<br /></i><i>艾米莉亚·佩雷斯（EmiliaPérez）<br /></i><i>我还在这里<br /></i><i>镍男孩<br /></i><i>物质<br /></i><i>邪恶</i></p><p><b>最佳导演</b></p><p><strong>Sean Baker,</strong> <strong>Anora – WINNER</strong><i><br /></i>布雷迪·科贝特（Brady Corbet），<i>野蛮主义者<br /></i>詹姆斯·曼戈尔德（James Mangold），<i>一个完全未知的<br /></i>Jacques Audiard， <i>EmiliaPérez<br /></i> Coralie Fargeat，<i>物质</i></p><p><b>Best Actor</b></p><p> <strong>Adrien Brody,</strong> <i><strong>The</strong></i> <strong>Brutalist – WINNER</strong><i><br /></i> TimothéeChalamet，<i>一个完全未知的<br /></i>科尔曼·多明哥（Colman Domingo），<i>唱歌<br /></i>拉尔夫·费恩斯（Ralph Fiennes），<i>会议<br /></i>Sebastian Stan <i>, The Apprentice</i></p><p><b>最好的女演员</b></p><p>辛西娅·埃里沃（Cynthia Erivo），<i>邪恶<br /></i>KarlaSofíaGascón， <i>EmiliaPérez<br /></i> <strong>Mikey Madison,</strong> <strong>Anora – WINNER</strong><i><br /></i>黛咪·摩尔（Demi Moore），<i>物质<br /></i>Fernanda Torres, <i>I&#39;m Still Here</i></p><p><b>最好的支持演员</b></p><p>Yura Borisov， <i>Anora<br /></i> <strong>Kieran Culkin,</strong> <i><strong>A Real Pain</strong></i> <